    • name

      public EntryBuilder name(String name)

      Sets the entry icon. This is required.

    • advancement

      public EntryBuilder advancement(String path)
      Sets an advancement needed to unlock the entry. The namespace is set to the namespace of the category, this entry belongs to.

    • advancement

      public EntryBuilder advancement(String namespace, String path)
      Sets an advancement needed to unlock the entry.

    • advancement

      public EntryBuilder advancement(net.minecraft.resources.ResourceLocation advancement)
      Sets an advancement needed to unlock the entry.

    • text

      public EntryBuilder text(String text)
      Adds some text content to this entry.

    • caption

      public EntryBuilder caption(String text)
      Adds some caption text content to the entry. Caption text behaves as regular text except when added right after a CaptionContent in which case the caption text will merge onto the previous content.

    • flip

      public EntryBuilder flip()
      Causes a page flip. That means no text after a flip will be put on a page that started before the flip.

    • flip

      public EntryBuilder flip(String anchor)
      Causes a page flip. That means no text after a flip will be put on a page that started before the flip. Also adds an anchor to the next page that is built, that can then be referenced by links inside the book.

    • image

      public EntryBuilder image(String title, String... images)
      Adds some images to the entry. The image namespaces are set to the namespace of the category, this entry belongs to.

    • image

      public EntryBuilder image(String title, net.minecraft.resources.ResourceLocation... images)
      Adds some images to the entry.

    • crafting

      public EntryBuilder crafting(String path)
      Adds a crafting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a crafting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • crafting

      public EntryBuilder crafting(String namespace, String path)
      Adds a crafting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a crafting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • crafting

      public EntryBuilder crafting(net.minecraft.resources.ResourceLocation id)
      Adds a crafting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a crafting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • smelting

      public EntryBuilder smelting(String path)
      Adds a smelting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a smelting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • smelting

      public EntryBuilder smelting(String namespace, String path)
      Adds a smelting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a smelting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • smelting

      public EntryBuilder smelting(net.minecraft.resources.ResourceLocation id)
      Adds a smelting recipe to the entry. If the previous content is a smelting recipe as well, they'll merge together and form a double recipe page.

    • item

      public EntryBuilder item(net.minecraft.world.level.ItemLike stack)
      Adds some spotlight content that displays an item. It will also link the recipe for that item and cause a page flip.

    • item

      public EntryBuilder item(net.minecraft.world.level.ItemLike stack, boolean linkRecipe)
      Adds some spotlight content that displays an item. It will also cause a page flip.

    • item

      public EntryBuilder item(net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack stack)
      Adds some spotlight content that displays an item. It will also link the recipe for that item and cause a page flip.

    • item

      public EntryBuilder item(net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack stack, boolean linkRecipe)
      Adds some spotlight content that displays an item. It will also cause a page flip.

    • entity

      public EntryBuilder entity(net.minecraft.world.entity.EntityType<?> entity)
      Adds some content to the entry that display the given entity.

    • multiblock

      public EntryBuilder multiblock(String title, String data)
      Adds some content to the entry that display a multiblock.
      Parameters:
      data - The multiblock data as recognised by patchouli.
